1. Ona je otišla na *mjestu* gdje nikad nije bila. (She went to a place where she had never been before.) 
2. *Mjestu* na kome se nalazim je veoma lijepo. (The place where I am is very nice.) 
3. Nisam znao da se njegov dom nalazi na tome *mjestu*. (I didn't know that his home was located there.) 
4. Ona je preselila na drugo *mjesto*. (She moved to another place.) 
5. On je tražio *mjesto* gdje može da živi. (He was looking for a place to live.)